+2 CHA, +8 WIS, +50 MANA<br />
WT: 1.0<br />
Class: CLR, SHM<br />
Race: HUM, BAR, ERU, HIE, DEF, HEF<br />
<br />
Once you have the key proceed to the mirror above the Mummy room and put your key on the mouse Cursor and hit U.<br />
<br />
Drops on this level:<br />
Various Gnome Skin Pieces<br />
Mummy Wrappings (just for sale)<br />
Various Crystallized Armor<br />
Various Crystallized, Fading Shadow, and Velium Weapons<br />
<br />
Fingerbone Hoop (Off Magot Infested Flesh)<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM <br />
AC: 2<br />
+3 DEX, +3 WIS, +3 AGI<br />
WT: 0.1<br />
Class: WAR, SHD, MNK, BRD, ROG, SHM<br />
Race: HUM, BAR, ERU, DEF, HEF, TRL, OGR, IKS<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
The Fifth Floor:<br />
-----------------<br />
<br />
When you port up the first thing you should notice is Golems in Ice Pillars. You have arrived as an unwanted guest at an Undead Wedding.<br />
<br />
Trap Warning: No traps on this level. Have fun.<br />
<br />
It would be best to explain the spawns first. <br />
<br />
Unlike the other floors, the rares always respawn in the same area, have no PH. <br />
<br />
On any of the kills the Keyholder can Instaspawn, the Keyholder is “An Enraged Relative” and the rares are “Nosja” and “Daman” but its best to point out Ceremonial Wedding swords drop off all the guests rarely. Drop Information for them as follows:<br />
<br />
An Enraged Relative:<br />
<br />
Bone Fingered Key (Always)<br />
<br />
Crystallized Shadow Belt (Uncommon)<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br />
AC: 1<br />
+1 CHA, +2 INT, +2 AGI, +10 HP, +5 MANA<br />
WT: 0.2<br />
Class: WAR, CLR, SHD, MNK, BRD, ROG, SHM<br />
Race: HUM, BAR, ERU, DEF, TRL, OGR, GNM, IKS<br />
<br />
