Rune Etched Wedding Band: (Rare)<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM <br />
AC: 2<br />
+3 STR, +4 STA, +6 AGI, +15 HP, +8 DR, +8 PR<br />
WT: 0.1<br />
Class: ALL<br />
Race: ALL<br />
<br />
<br />
How to tackle this floor:<br />
<br />
Proceed to pull the Golems two at a time or if you have a high level with you have them hit them with a spell and single pull them. <br />
<br />
Once all the Golems are pulled Proceed to the opening to the wedding. Rest here at the door and you have many choices. You can either pull the wedding guests all at once and AoE them or you can try to pull a little at a time. These are pretty low level (half green to 40 half blue) try to kill them all first. <br />
<br />
Now you should have the bride (Daman), the groom (Nosaj), the priest, two undead dancers, and a spawn or two in the back.<br />
If you have a high level, single the Groom, then the Bride, then the Priest. If not pull them and kill in this order: Priest first, then Nosja, then Daman. Priest is a Cleric, Nosja is a Necromancer, and Daman is a Shadowknight (Harmtouch)<br />
<br />
Kill all the rest in the room then you have several options:<br />
<br />
(1 Stay in the room and wait for repop Ignoring the back spawn eg. Golems<br />
(2 Move back to port in and kill them as above.<br />
(3 Stay in room and pull out the cubbies<br />
(4 go upstairs and camp the Golems Above while waiting for repop.<br />
<br />
Or a combination of that.<br />
<br />
Once you have the key and wish to go ahead to level 6, Proceed to the Side room with Golem Ushers in it. Bout 1/4 of the way around the circle going counterclockwise from the zonein put the key on your cursor and hit U. <br />
<br />
The Mirror Out:<br />
The mirror out on this floor is very simple, when you port in turn around and it’s on the wall behind you.<br />
<br />
<br />
Drops on this level:<br />
<br />
Bone Fingered Key<br />
<br />
Crystallized Shadow Belt<br />
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <br />
