		<div><br /> Ro's Fiery Sundering works very well against Tserrina. With it active, 2 of 2 Starfires stuck for full damage. Ro's faded while I was casting the third Starfire - that one did all of 24 damage! <img src="http://thedruidsgrove.org/forums/images/smilies/tongue.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Stick Out Tongue" class="inlineimg" /><br />
<br />
And if you don't have the spell yet, chances are good you'll pick it up on your way up to the 7th floor.<br />
<br />
Also, Tserrina drops a 'master key' that uses the left-hand mirror on floor one. It ports the group to a mirror room (I think on the 7th floor). It has 6 mirrors around the room; each one supposedly leads to one of the other floors directly. My group needs to experiment with this a bit more to figure out which mirrors go where.<br />
